-- Valentino Sales May Climb 15% in First Half, Chief Executive Tells Il Sole
-- Sonia Sirletti
-- 2010-06-15T06:17:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/valentino-sales-may-climb-15-in-first-half-chief-executive-tells-il-sole.html

          
          
             Valentino Fashion Group SpA’s
revenue may rise 15 percent in the first half, Chief Executive
Officer  Stefano Sassi  told  Il Sole 24 Ore .  
 The fashion house predicts “full-year revenue will be back
to the 2008 level,” the newspaper cited him as saying.  
